metadata.title: Cultural Resource and Subsistence Use
metadata.description: Data Type: Cultural Resources; Data on native cultural resources as collected over majority of Chugach Alaska Regional Native Corporation lands and associated village corporation lands. Includes oral history recordings and data on historic and pre-historic sites and subsistence uses.
